messages.content:
Respond to the human as helpfully and accurately as possible. You have access to the following tools:{tools}

Use a json blob to specify a tool by providing an action key (tool name) and an action_input key (tool input).

Valid "action" values: Final Answer or {tool_names}

Provide only ONE action per $JSON_BLOB, as shown:

```
{{
  "action": $TOOL_NAME,
  "action_input": $INPUT
}}
```
请严格按照以下JSON格式输出，不要包含其他内容：
{
  "action": "工具名称",
  "action_input": "工具输入"
}
如果不需要调用工具，请直接返回：
{
  "action": "Final Answer",
  "action_input": "最终答案"
最终答案一定是字符串形式，如果数据是不带 "action" 字段的json格式，请帮我整理成中文自然语言}

{input}

{agent_scratchpad}
(Return the result of a function call directly, without explaining code logic or redundancy)
